l="nofollow"&gt;https://x.com/nick_tikhonov&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr /&gt;&lt;p&gt;评论网址： &lt;a href="https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=47224295"&gt;https://news.ycombinator.com/item?&lt;/a&gt; id=47224295&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;积分：549&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; # 评论: 152&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Mar 2026 21:23:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.ntik.me/posts/voice-agent</guid></item><item><title>欢迎（回到）Macintosh</title><link>https://take.surf/2026/03/01/welcome-back-to-macintosh</link><description>&lt;p&gt;文章网址： &lt;a href="https://take.surf/2026/03/01/welcome-back-to-macintosh"&gt;https://take.surf/2026/03/01/welcome-back-to-macintosh&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;评论网址： &lt;a href="https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=47224118"&gt;https://news.ycombinator.com/item?&lt;/a&gt; id=47224118&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;积分：321&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; # 评论：258&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Mar 2026 21:09:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://take.surf/2026/03/01/welcome-back-to-macintosh</guid></item><item><title>不列颠哥伦比亚省永久采用夏令时</title><link>https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/british-columbia/b-c-adopting-year-round-daylight-time-9.7111657</link><description>&lt;p&gt;文章网址： &lt;a href="https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/british-columbia/b-c-adopting-year-round-daylight-time-9.7111657"&gt;https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/british-columbia/bc-adopting-year-round-daylight-time-9.7111657&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;评论网址： &lt;a href="https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=47223620"&gt;https://news.ycombinator.com/item?&lt;/a&gt; id=47223620&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;积分：1106&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; # 评论: 542&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Mar 2026 20:30:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/british-columbia/b-c-adopting-year-round-daylight-time-9.7111657</guid></item><item><title>显示 HN：uBlock 过滤器列表以模糊所有 Instagram 卷轴</title><link>https://gist.github.com/shraiwi/009c652da6ce8c99a6e1e0c86fe66886</link><description>&lt;p&gt;uBO 的过滤器列表，可模糊 