scription>&lt;p&gt;文章网址： &lt;a href="https://github.com/anthropics/claude-code/issues/22543"&gt;https://github.com/anthropics/claude-code/issues/22543&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;评论网址： &lt;a href="https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=47218288"&gt;https://news.ycombinator.com/item?&lt;/a&gt; id=47218288&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;积分：370&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; # 评论: 186&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Mar 2026 14:21:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://github.com/anthropics/claude-code/issues/22543</guid></item><item><title>新款 iPad Air，由 M4 提供动力</title><link>https://www.apple.com/newsroom/2026/03/apple-introduces-the-new-ipad-air-powered-by-m4/</link><description>&lt;p&gt;文章网址： &lt;a href="https://www.apple.com/newsroom/2026/03/apple-introduces-the-new-ipad-air-powered-by-m4/"&gt;https://www.apple.com/newsroom/2026/03/apple-introduces-the-new-ipad-air-powered-by-m4/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;评论网址： &lt;a href="https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=47218175"&gt;https://news.ycombinator.com/item?&lt;/a&gt; id=47218175&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;积分：432&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; # 评论: 669&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Mar 2026 14:11:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.apple.com/newsroom/2026/03/apple-introduces-the-new-ipad-air-powered-by-m4/</guid></item><item><title>iPhone 17e</title><link>https://www.apple.com/newsroom/2026/03/apple-introduces-iphone-17e/</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.apple.com/iphone-17e/" rel="nofollow"&gt;https://www.apple.com/iphone-17e/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr /&gt;&lt;p&gt;评论网址： &lt;a href="https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=47218084"&gt;https://news.ycombinator.com/item?&lt;/a&gt; id=47218084&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;积分：317&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; # 评论：492&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Mar 2026 14:03:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.apple.com/newsroom/2026/03/apple-introduces-iphone-17e/</guid></item></channel></rss>